      <notes>+ Implemented the functionality of junitour (http://junitour.sourceforge.net/).

+ Added scripts for convenient CLI invocation of the PHPUnit2_TextUI.

* PHPUnit2_Framework_Assert::assertType() can now be used with objects as well.

  (Patch by Jeremiah Jacks &lt;jjacks@tamiya.com&gt;)

