* Changed PHPUnit_* class names to PHPUnit2_* and the base installation directory from &quot;PHPUnit&quot; to &quot;PHPUnit2&quot; to allow for parallel installation of PHPUnit 1.x and PHPUnit 2.x.

! PHP 5.0.0-RC2 (or later) is now required.

      
